<p>[Legal Entity Name] ("d'Skills," "we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect through dskills.io (the "Services"), how we use and protect it, and the choices available to you.</p>
